"affirmation_desc_five" : "EXERCISE - Today just pick one area of life where you struggle and try to think about all the beliefs that might be holding you from doing the best in that area. Write them down and burn or flush that piece of paper. And Write the new beliefs that you want to acquire! 

(TAKE ACTION IMMEDIATELY,DO THE EXERCISE NOW WHETHER YOU FEEL LIKE IT OR NOT)"

"affirmation_desc_four" : "Following are the points you should consider while writing your affirmations: 
1. Your affirmations must be short but well defined. 
2.It must be positive. (Example - say you want to be financially independent, then you can write affirmation like 'I am wealthy' rather than 'I've cleared all my debts now' your subconscious can't differentiate what you want or don't want) 
3.It must be in PRESENT STATE(this is important). 
4. You must mix positive emotions and visualization with it,plain unemotional words don't influence you mind. 
5.Focus on 5-8 affirmations and then add new one slowly. 
6. And most important one be consistent! You can only rewire your brain by constant repetition.(repeat your affirmations at least twice a day)"
"affirmation_desc_one" : "Affirmations are short and well defined positive statements written in present tense."

"affirmation_desc_three" : "You'll be repeating affirmations daily. They are a great way to form new beliefs. Don't get tricked by the simplicity of the idea. Affirmations when mixed with feeling of faith are extremely powerful you can actually rewire your brain through the daily practices given here. Whatever maybe your beliefs are right now understand that it has been instilled from your parents and society.

(This video covers everything you need to understand about the affirmations)"

"affirmation_desc_two" : "Following are the statements of the classic 'THINK AND GROW RICH' by Napoleon Hill - 

 'It is a well known fact that one comes, finally to believe whatever one repeats to one's self, whether the statements be true of false. If a man repeats a lie over and over, he will eventually accept the lie as truth. 
Moreover, he will believe it to be the truth.

 You are suggested to read the above paragraph at least twice and make sure you absorb the POWERFUL INFORMATION laid out here."

"affirmations_are_a_great_way_to_form_new_beliefs_it_is_a_well_known_fact_that_anything_we_repeat_to_our_self_wether_that_statements_be_true_of_false_one_comes_finally_to_believe_it_nnot_only_that_he_she_believes_it_to_be_truth_n_nnow_if_you_will_not_choose_what_you_want_to_believe_you_ll_be_using_this_power_against_you_n_nso_make_sure_you_repeat_this_powerful_exercise_everyday_making_a_habit_of_it_is_very_essential" : "Affirmations are a great way to form new beliefs. It is a well known fact that anything we repeat to our-self whether that statements be true or false one comes finally to believe it. Not only that he/she believes it to be truth.

Now if you will not choose what you want to believe you'll be using this power against you. So make sure you repeat this powerful exercise everyday. Making a habit of it is very essential."

"by_may_10th_2020" : "By may 10th 2020, I will have in my possession $100K. 
To achieve my goal, I will be doing be doing my best as a content creator and provide value to the people.

Or

 By 5th July 2018, I will be losing 25lbs weight. To achieve my goal I will give my best in gym and I will follow a strict diet."
"common_google_play_services_unknown_issue" : "%1$s is having trouble with Google Play services. Please try again."

"day_desc_2" : "As you repeat anything for more than 90 days it becomes part of your LIFESTYLE. So if you can reach there then definitely you’ll be living your life with a totally new and positive mindset. If you miss more than 2 days your streak will be reset to 21."
"day_desc_3" : "And there you’re living a new lifestyle try and keep this new habit for a year. If you miss more than 1 day your streak will be reset to 91."
"day_desc_4" : "Congratulations! you just finished a whole year. You’re are on a new level just keep on going."
"days_desc_one" : "It is said that anything you do for 21 days becomes a habit. It is very essential that you do all mental exercises here for 21 days, if you miss any day you’ll be back to 0."

"desc_pay_attention_closely" : "As you will be following daily practice given here, you will be making your Subconscious mind more receptive to the thoughts related to your goal. And you'll be having by some mysterious way a plan or inspiration for achieving your goal. DO NOT DENY THAT! Make sure as soon as you have it NOTE IT DOWN IMMEDIATELY. AND PUT THAT PLAN INTO ACTION, EVEN IF YOU DON'T THINK YOU CAN'T RIGHT NOW."

"description_21_days_finish" : "It is very important to thank yourself because, most of the people quit before reaching this point. You not only decided what you want to accomplish but, you're also taking steps to actually making it happen!"
"fact_21_days" : "In fact, less than 5% of the people actually have a written goal."

"finish_off_by_a_positive_video" : "How about finishing with a positive video!
 we've gathered videos that will help you have better understanding and new perspective.
And we highly recommend that you do watch it."

"finish_off_by_visualization_nthink_about_every_small_detail_and_picture_it_in_your_mind_think_about_the_person_you_want_to_become_ngather_as_many_photos_as_you_can_to_help_you_visualize_better" : "Finish off by visualization... Think about every small detail and picture it in your mind, think about the person you want to become. Gather as many photos as you can to help you visualize better!"
"harness_power_of_visualization_to_influence_your_subconscious_mind_even_faster" : "Harness power of visualization to influence your subconscious mind even faster."
"i_am_so_happy_and_grateful_now_that" : "(I am so happy and grateful now that)"

"i_know_i_ve_the_ability_to_achieve_any_goal_that_i_set_for_myself_and_will_keep_on_trying_no_matter_what_till_i_achieve_it_every_day_my_desire_is_getting_stronger_day_by_day_i_can_already_see_my_self_having_achieved_that_goal" : "I know I've the ability to achieve any goal that I set for myself, and will keep on trying no matter what till I ACHIEVE IT! Every day my DESIRE IS GETTING STRONGER day by day. I can already see my self having achieved that goal."

"i_repeated_my_goal_out_loud_at_least_3_times_in_front_of_a_mirror_and_imagined_my_self_already_having_achieved_the_goal" : "I repeated my goal out loud at least 3 times in front of a mirror and imagined my self already having achieved the goal."

"i_understand_that_this_practice_i_am_forming_new_beliefs_i_know_that_whatever_i_think_repeatedly_influences_my_beliefs_and_actions_in_real_life" : "I understand that i've unlimited potential and the only limits that i've are because of my negative beliefs, As I am repeating affirmations everyday I am reinforcing new and positive beliefs in my sub-conscious mind. And I am now tapping into my fullest potential."

"once_you_have_a_definite_goal_now_decide_in_what_time_span_you_want_to_achieve_it_make_sure_you_have_exact_date_n_nand_finally_what_are_you_willing_to_do_in_order_to_achieve_your_goal_this_is_very_important" : "Once you have a DEFINITE GOAL. Now decide in what time span you want to achieve it,make sure you have exact date. And finally what are you willing to do in order to achieve your goal.(This is very important!)"
"s2" : "Allow Ad to store image in Picture gallery?"
"s6" : "Allow Ad to create a calendar event?"
"think_and" : "Napoleon Hill had taught in his book, 'Think and Grow Rich'. One can achieve any goal by following this four principle!"

"think_for_sometime_over_the_following_question_n_njust_suppose_if_everything_you_want_achieve_is_possible_what_it_is_that_you_want_the_most_n_nit_is_not_necessary_that_you_believe_it_right_now_n_n_but_just_think_about_it_and_write_it_down_somewhere_n_nwhat_is_it_that_you_truly_want" : "Think for a second over the following...
 What would you do or want if you were guaranteed to achieve/have it. It is not necessary that you believe it right now? But just think about it and write it down somewhere... 

What is it that you truly want?"

"visualization_desc_one" : "Having a vision board makes visualization a lot more effective easy and fun. Our subconscious mind only thinks in terms of images. It is recommended that you find at least 4-7 pictures of whatever it is that you want. It is a great way of visualising your goals."

"visualization_desc_three" : "Your subconscious mind can't make a difference between what you imagine or what is real, this is what makes visualisation very powerful tool. You are requested to watch the video given below where Tony Robbins describes the power of visualization through a practical exercise which you can do right now! 

(GO AND WATCH THE VIDEO NOW AND PERFORM THE ACTIVITY HE SHOWS,YOU'LL BE AMAZED)"

"visualization_desc_two" : "Some of you might be amazed to know that the famous hollywood actor 'Jim Carrey' used to do visualisation. Not only that he wrote himself a cheque of $10 Million for acting.
